column2: SELECT TOP #  S.ObjID, S.SpecZ,  &&&, L2.ew ,L2.ewErr  &&&,L3.ew,L3.ewErr FROM QsoSpec AS S   JOIN SpecLine AS L2 ON S.SpecObjID = L2.SpecObjID  JOIN SpecLine AS L3 ON S.SpecObjID = L3.SpecObjID WHERE L2.LineId = # and L3.LineID = # and (specclass=# or specclass=#) and S.SpecZconf > .# and S.SpecZ < .#
